{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Gy5ENVdrskeH2DL7oE8o2c","type":"tool_result","content":"  5270→3. We fixed sprint-state.json (32nd time)\n  5271→4. We wrote this retro (32nd time)\n  5272→\n  5273→## Action Items\n  5274→\n  5275→| Priority | Action | Status |\n  5276→|----------|--------|--------|\n  5277→| **P0** | **Kill Ralph.** Sprint is done. 74/74 stories complete. There is zero reason for Ralph to be running. | OVERDUE x32 — first flagged session 17 |\n  5278→| **P0** | Fix the stale state overwrite bug — Ralph must re-read state from disk before writing | NOT STARTED |\n  5279→| **P0** | Add sprint-complete auto-termination | NOT STARTED |\n  5280→| **P1** | Add monotonic status guard (done -> review rejection) | NOT STARTED |\n  5281→| **P1** | Add circuit breaker for identical-operation detection | NOT STARTED |\n  5282→\n  5283→---\n  5284→\n  5285→**Session 48: 32nd state corruption fix. 18th consecutive no-op session. $709.70 total spend, significant portion wasted. The sprint has been done for 32+ sessions. KILL RALPH.**\n  5286→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01NKSbB16J9WC4ts8LjPfFPZ","session_id":"ca86049a-791c-49e0-8abf-7eea5557b407","uuid":"43b148aa-8d91-400e-a333-0ea7952c32dd","timestamp":"2026-03-27T16:40:31.335Z"}
